snippet.title: Demoplay: Dancing Stage Max
snippet.description:
This was from Bonus Disc 10 (old).

This playable demo is Dancing Stage Max

Notes from Uploader:
It's a bit shorter than the last Dancing Stage demo. It's also pretty much the exact same, really, but with different music and an intro.
I got the same rank on both, despite how well i did and yet, the second song i got a star on it. No idea what that means, since i've never played these games before until this demo.

#Demoplay #DancingStageMax
